name: Rags to Riches
description:
TO MAKE A TRANSACTION SIMPLY CLICK THE "ORDER" OPTION, THEN PRESS ADD TO CART, CHOOSE UK FOR SHIPPING, GO TO THE CHECKOUT, YOU WILL BE INSTRUCTED TO LOG IN TO PAYPAL, HOWEVER IF YOU TURN YOUR ATENTION TO THE BOTTOM LEFT HAND SIDE OF THE PAGE YOU WILL SEE A LINK THAT DIRECTS YOU TO A DEBIT/CREDIT CARD PAGE. EVERYTHING IS 100% PAYPAL SECURE, BUT THE BENEFITS ARE YOU DON'T REQUIRE A PAYPAL TO PAY!

Thankyou kindly for your custom.

name: wow!! konichiwa clothing
description:
CHECKOUT FOR T-SHIRTS.

To place an order simply select your option, go to checkout, choose UK for shipping, you will then be directed to a page that asks you to log in to Paypal, please ignore this and turn your direction towards the lower left hand corner where you will see a link to pay securely by credit/debit card.

Thanks very much for your custom.

name: OVER DRIVE PROMOTIONS
description:
Checkout for t-shirts. Price includes t-shirts, printing, delivery and card charge.

INSTRUCTIONS:
Go to checkout.
Choose UK for shipping.
When you come to a page showing Paypal log-in details, please turn your attention towards the bottom left hand side of the page, there will be a relatiively inconspicuous link that allows you to order via ANY credit or debit card, alternatively simply log-in to your paypal.

Thankyou kindly for your custom.
